    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been an absolute joy to drive and has been really well-looked after over the years. It runs like a dream and is perfect for anyone looking for a reliable, comfy car that\u2019s ready to hit the road today. It\u2019s got a few minor signs of love here and there, but overall it\u2019s in great shape and ready for many more adventures. Come take it for a spin\u2014I know you'll love it as much as I have!",
