    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a purist-spec driver featuring the high-revving S54B32 power plant equipped with individual throttle bodies. Power is delivered via a Getrag 420G 6-speed manual gearbox to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The vehicle has undergone significant preventative maintenance, including a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement to ensure internal longevity. The chassis is structurally sound with documented subframe reinforcement, and the suspension maintains factory-spec kinematics with upgraded polyurethane bushings. While the exterior shows honest road wear, the mechanical vitals are dialed in for high-performance use.",
      "price": 34500.0,
