    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained luxury sedan that strikes the perfect balance between high-end performance and daily practicality. This vehicle has been treated with consistent care, primarily serving as a reliable highway commuter. The exterior maintains a deep, lustrous finish, though observant buyers will find minor, expected stone chips on the front fascia consistent with regular road use. Inside, the smoke-free cabin features premium leather upholstery that remains supple and supportive, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All onboard electronics, including the navigation system, dual-zone climate control, and premium audio, function flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in excellent health; it comes with a documented service history, including a recent comprehensive multi-point inspection and a fresh oil change. The tires offer plenty of tread for the seasons ahead, and the suspension remains firm and responsive. This is an ideal opportunity for a discerning buyer to own a sophisticated, well-cared-for vehicle that delivers a smooth and confident driving experience.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
