    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, a testament to both engineering excellence and diligent ownership. This unit has undergone a rigorous professional inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and aesthetic standards that surpass typical market offerings. Featuring a refined interior and a robust powertrain, it provides a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning professional. This vehicle represents a premier opportunity to acquire a high-caliber automobile that balances superior performance with long-term value.",
      "price": 36500.0,
