    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm looking for a new home for my trusty car, and I think you're going to love it! It's been so reliable for me and is still in really wonderful shape. It drives like a dream and has been kept very tidy. If you're looking for a solid, well-cared-for ride that's ready for many more miles of memories, this is the one for you! Come take it for a test drive and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
