    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound E92 M3, a definitive example of high-revving atmospheric performance. At its heart lies the S65 4.0L V8, delivering a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline. This chassis is equipped with a tactile 6-speed manual transmission and the Variable M Differential Lock, ensuring precise torque vectoring. Critical preventative maintenance has been addressed, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service, ensuring the VANOS system and valvetrain remain in peak operating condition. The Electronic Damping Control (EDC) provides sharp transient response, while the subframe and bushings remain tight. While the paint retains a minor road patina, the structural and mechanical integrity of this M-car makes it an ideal candidate for the discerning driver who prioritizes drivetrain excellence and engineering purity.",
